## Objective
Create a responsive landing page with an interactive navigation menu that enhances the user experience across devices.

## Task Details
- Implement a **navigation menu** that:
  - Changes **color or style** when scrolled or when hovering over any menu item.
  - Remains in a **fixed position** and is visible on all pages.

## Features
- Responsive layout for all screen sizes.
- Sticky navigation bar.
- Hover and scroll effects on menu items.
- Clean and modern design.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS

